FORMAT: 1A
HOST: http://api.tinkerware.io

# Users API
An API that manages the resources of an User inside our API

# Group Users
User management

## Users Collection [/api/v1/users]
### Register an user [POST]
+ Request (application/json)

    {
      "user": {
        "name": "Leonel Roberto",
        "username": "iLeonelRoberto",
        "email": "some@email.com",
        "password": "somepassword"
      }
    }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    {
      "username": "iLeonelRoberto",
      "token": "GSjtfp4Gdrb5OovWSrVEwy78fe2IhbHmGcaYmSN8IQp5dxeJcH4wH8qDt3ut2Ulu"
    }

## User Collection [/api/v1/users/{id}]
+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... `id` of the user

### Get an User [GET]
+ Request

    + Header

            authorization: Bearer qphYSqjEFk1RcFxYqqIIFk4vaBJvDoBr3t9aHTp1JFEAO0NS7ECyLJJyUPybOUNf

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "user": {
            "id": 1,
            "name": "Leonel Roberto",
            "username": "iLeonelRoberto",
            "email": "some@email.com"
          }
        }

# Group Login
