# Group Integration
Manages the different integrations an user has for the platform (ir. Github, Facebook, etc.)

## Integrations Collection [/api/v1/users/{userid}/integration]
+ Parameters
    + userid (required, number, `1`) ... `userid` of the user

### Add a new Integration [POST]
+ Request (application/json)

    + Header

            authorization: Bearer qphYSqjEFk1RcFxYqqIIFk4vaBJvDoBr3t9aHTp1JFEAO0NS7ECyLJJyUPybOUNf

    + Body

            {
              "integration": {
                "id": 1,
                "user_id": 1,
                "token": "QTD1EKoYQj7Qtw2EFRN1R8gUvdB3f5Y4BWN3N9NSqWktWFnYTX5LNlxaMRilSG2l",
                "provider": "github",
